309 likes, 8 comments - age_undreamed_of on December 28, 2023: "#MichaelShea 

The Incompleat Nifft, by Michael Shea.

If you're having trouble tracking down the first two books in the Nifft series, you might have better luck picking up this Omnibus version.

This title collects Nifft the Lean, and The Mines of Behemoth.

Baen Books, 2000.
Cover art by Bary Ruddell.
